Arabia, Egypt, Pakistan, Turkey, Cuba, Iran, the Democratic
People's Republic of Korea, Iraq, Morocco, Laos and Vietnam.
</P>
<P>
The bill is seeking to divest the city's funds from banks that
operate in the countries, as well as to prohibit the city from
awarding contracts to firms operating in them. 
