24.5 million U.S. dollars from two financial bodies of the United
Arab Emirates (UAE).
</P>
<P>
This was announced after Jordanian Prime Minister Abdul-Salam
Majali returned home this evening from his three-day official
visit to the UAE, Radio Jordan reported.
</P>
