<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, June 24 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese People's Liberation
Army (PLA) delegation, led by Commander of Beijing Military Area
Command General Li Laizhu, completed their visit to Slovakia and
left for home today.
</P>
