<HEADLINE> Jordan's King Invited to OIC Summit in Iran </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, June 24 (Xinhua) -- Iran's President Hashemi Rafsanjani
will send a special envoy to deliver his invitation to Jordanian
King Hussein for him to attend the summit of the Organization of
Islamic Conference to be held in Tehran in December.
</P>
<P>
