regarded the Jordanian king as pro-U.S. and a close friend of
Israel, observers here said.
</P>
<P>
Iran's late spiritual leader Imam Khomeini attacked the king
for his support of Iraq during the eight-year Iran-Iraq war
(1980-88).
</P>
<P>
Iran has already invited more than 20 heads of state of Islamic
countries to attend the summit, apparently in a bid to expand its
influence in the Islamic world.
</P>
<P>
Leaders of 42 Muslim countries are expected to be present at
the OIC summit. The construction of a luxurious palace for the
historical event is near completion. 
