construction: water and electricity supply, road building, and
water conservancy. An aquatic product wholesale market with a
yearly trade volume of 50 million yuan was also established in the
zone.
</P>
<P>
The zone received investors from a dozen countries and regions
including the United States, Japan, the Netherlands, Italy, and
Australia.
</P>
<P>
The World Bank loaned 3.8 million US dollars to the zone to
develop aquatic products. 
