Shanghai Haixing Shipping Co., Ltd, which will take effect on July 1.
</P>
<P>
The Shanghai Haixing shipping Co., Ltd, is the only inland
shipping company that has listed its H shares in Hong Kong. The 76
cargo vessels of its fleet have been insured.
</P>
