<HEADLINE> Shipping and Marine Engineering College for Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 24 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai's 100-year-old Jiaotong
University, one of China's most prestigious institutes of higher
learning, has set up a college of shipping and marine engineering.
</P>
<P>
The college was established by the Shipbuilding Department,
which has graduated more than 5,000 engineers in the 54 years
since its founding in 1943. Many of its graduates play major roles
in scientific study.
</P>
<P>
The department has had 91 scientific and technological
development projects that won national awards.
</P>
<P>
The college has two departments, six research institutes, a
state key lab, and a ship engineering center. 
