<HEADLINE> Johnson to Return to Compete in Paris </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, June 23 (Xinhua) -- Olympic champion Michael
Johnson, recovering from a leg injury, has decided to return to
competition at the Paris grand prix meeting on Wednesday, his
agent said on Monday.
</P>
<P>
