150-meter one-on-one showdown against 100-meter world record
holder Donovan Bailey in Toronto on June 1.
</P>
<P>
Johnson is also expected to compete in other European meetings
in the coming weeks.
</P>
<P>
The 200-meter world record holder is scheduled to run 400
meters at Sheffield, England, on Sunday and at Lausanne on July
2. 
